@startuml sequence_notification
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Real-Time Notification Delivery

actor "Fleet Manager" as User
participant "Angular SPA\n(Kendo UI)" as FE
participant "NotificationsController\n(.NET 8+)" as API
participant "NotificationDispatch\nService" as Dispatch
participant "NotificationHub\n(SignalR)" as Hub
participant "Azure Logic Apps" as LA
database "SQL Server 2022" as DB

== Notification Trigger (e.g., Critical Alert) ==
Dispatch -> DB: Store Notification record
Dispatch -> Hub: Push to user group
Hub -> FE: ReceiveNotification event
FE -> FE: Update bell badge count
FE --> User: Toast + badge update

== Email/SMS (if preference enabled) ==
Dispatch -> DB: Check NotificationPreference
Dispatch -> LA: Trigger email/SMS workflow
LA -> LA: Send email/SMS

== User Views Notifications ==
User -> FE: Click notification bell
FE -> API: GET /api/v1/notifications
API -> DB: Query by UserId, ordered
DB --> API: Notification list
API --> FE: Paginated notifications
FE --> User: Dropdown with notifications

== Mark as Read ==
User -> FE: Click notification
FE -> API: PUT /api/v1/notifications/{id}/read
API -> DB: Update IsRead = true
FE -> API: GET /api/v1/notifications/unread-count
API --> FE: Updated count
FE --> User: Navigate to entity

@enduml
